Chico Hamilton Trio Introducing Freddie Gambrell is an album by drummer and bandleader Chico Hamilton, released on the World Pacific label.[1][2][3]

Reception

[edit]

Professional ratingsReview scoresSourceRatingAllMusic[4]

AllMusic rated the album 2 stars.[4]

"Reservation Blues" (Freddie Gambrell) - 4:51

"Ex-Ray's Friends" (Gambrell) - 4:06

"Midnight Sun" (Lionel Hampton, Sonny Burke, Johnny Mercer) - 4:40
